Thank you for these excellent comments, Arkuun, and belated thanks for coming here in the first place. I am sure that you will make a valuable contribution. You are quite correct that authority and credentials are not the same thing. This probably comes up at least as often in the academic world as it did in the military. One of the classic problems in my field is devising a way to brief important legislators on our research without insulting their intelligence or losing them along the way.<br>
